  "detailed_description": "<h1>Special Offer</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hello! Do you have half a grand? What if I do?</h2><br>Take on the role of a thug: snatch a cell phone from the local bartender and take selfies with it like all proper thugs.<br>Go get some sigs at the local shop and hang out with the homeless.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389240/extras/a894c27d28c4d2b2a96682c8c4c0b7bb.poster.avif?t=1769829999\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389240/extras/a894c27d28c4d2b2a96682c8c4c0b7bb.webm?t=1769829999\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389240/extras/a894c27d28c4d2b2a96682c8c4c0b7bb.mp4?t=1769829999\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Walk around the neighborhood, talk to the cops, find notes from your friend Sergei that you drank with yesterday.<br>You can also piss on the door of the annoying neighbor who constantly plays his annoying music.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389240/extras/eaac77678e5f5de086c8b3085c684976.poster.avif?t=1769829999\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389240/extras/eaac77678e5f5de086c8b3085c684976.webm?t=1769829999\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389240/extras/eaac77678e5f5de086c8b3085c684976.mp4?t=1769829999\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>And don't forget to punish the utilities that don't want to do their job properly. <br>And do the rest!<br><br>You'll also get a lot of memes and references!",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hello! Do you have half a grand? What if I do?</h2><br>Take on the role of a thug: snatch a cell phone from the local bartender and take selfies with it like all proper thugs.<br>Go get some sigs at the local shop and hang out with the homeless.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389240/extras/a894c27d28c4d2b2a96682c8c4c0b7bb.poster.avif?t=1769829999\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389240/extras/a894c27d28c4d2b2a96682c8c4c0b7bb.webm?t=1769829999\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389240/extras/a894c27d28c4d2b2a96682c8c4c0b7bb.mp4?t=1769829999\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Walk around the neighborhood, talk to the cops, find notes from your friend Sergei that you drank with yesterday.<br>You can also piss on the door of the annoying neighbor who constantly plays his annoying music.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389240/extras/eaac77678e5f5de086c8b3085c684976.poster.avif?t=1769829999\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389240/extras/eaac77678e5f5de086c8b3085c684976.webm?t=1769829999\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389240/extras/eaac77678e5f5de086c8b3085c684976.mp4?t=1769829999\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>And don't forget to punish the utilities that don't want to do their job properly. <br>And do the rest!<br><br>You'll also get a lot of memes and references!",
